channel.title: What would you like me to produce?
channel.description:
This is my soundcloud page https://m.soundcloud.com/pistol69
As you can see most of my tunes are DnB with the exception of 1 Future Bass track and 1 Neuro Hop WIP.
I’m looking to expand and try other genres, What genre would you guys suggest that I have a go at producing?
